    S.sort()
    mp = {e: i for (i, e) in enumerate(S)}
    T = scores[:]
    T.sort()
    mpm = {e: i for (i, e) in enumerate(T)}
    INF = 10 ** 9 - 1
    ps = []

    results = []

                z = mp[y]
                idx = bisect(ps, z - 1)
                ps = ps[:idx] + [z] + ps[idx:]

            y = scores[x - 1]
            D[y] -= 1
            if D[y] == 0:
                z = mp[y]
                idx = bisect(ps, z - 1)
                ps.pop(idx)
        elif t == 'CHECK':
            left = -1
            right = INF
            while left + 1 < right:
                mid = left + right >> 1
                prv = -1
                cnt = 0
                for e in ps:
                    s = S[e]
                    v = mpm[s]
                    idx = max(bisect(T, s - mid - 1) - 1, prv)
                    cnt += v - idx
                    prv = v
                if N - cnt <= x:
                    right = mid
                else:
                    left = mid
            if right == INF:
                results.append('NA')
            else:
                results.append(right)
